1024
00:54:42,920 --> 00:54:43,920
 da znamo,

1025
00:54:43,920 --> 00:54:45,460
 da je Isus umro,

1026
00:54:45,460 --> 00:54:46,840
 da je uskrsnuo,

1027
00:54:46,840 --> 00:54:47,900
