1030
00:54:53,040 --> 00:54:54,580
 U onim događajima.

1031
00:54:54,580 --> 00:54:55,700
 I oni događaju nama.

1032
00:54:57,320 --> 00:54:58,540
 Ono što je fascinantno,

1033
00:54:58,540 --> 00:55:01,100
 bilo smo tamo razmatrali za vrijeme mise,

1034
00:55:01,100 --> 00:55:02,360
 mi stvarno vjerujemo

1035
00:55:02,360 --> 00:55:04,000
 da kada se Evanđelje navješta

1036
00:55:04,000 --> 00:55:04,840
 za vrijeme mise

1037
00:55:04,840 --> 00:55:07,700
 ili u sklopu neke liturgijske molitve,

1038
00:55:07,700 --> 00:55:08,900
 kao što je liturgija riječi

1039
00:55:08,900 --> 00:55:09,560
 ili sprovod

1040
00:55:09,560 --> 00:55:10,620
 ili neki sakramenat,

1041
00:55:10,620 --> 00:55:12,020
 mi vjerujemo

1042
00:55:12,020 --> 00:55:13,440
 da je taj dio

1043
00:55:13,440 --> 00:55:14,740
 Evanđelja koji se čita

1044
00:55:14,740 --> 00:55:15,640
 da se u tom trenutku

1045
00:55:15,640 --> 00:55:16,600
 ostvaruje.

1046
00:55:16,600 --> 00:55:18,960
 Znači, ako danas slušamo

1047
00:55:18,960 --> 00:55:19,600
 apostolema,

1048
00:55:19,600 --> 00:55:20,840
 negdje je Isus nekog pozvao.

1049
00:55:20,840 --> 00:55:22,540
 Nije to jedino,

1050
00:55:22,540 --> 00:55:23,280
 može ga on pozvati

1051
00:55:23,280 --> 00:55:24,280
 i po nekoj drugoj riječi.

1052
00:55:24,280 --> 00:55:24,880
 Naravno da je

1053
00:55:24,880 --> 00:55:25,580
 Božje milost,

1054
00:55:25,580 --> 00:55:26,360
 srđaj snaga,

1055
00:55:26,360 --> 00:55:27,140
 kreativnost

1056
00:55:27,140 --> 00:55:28,800
 neograničena.

1057
00:55:28,800 --> 00:55:30,020
 Ali mi vjerujemo

1058
00:55:30,020 --> 00:55:31,000
 da se to ostvaruje.

1059
00:55:31,000 --> 00:55:32,740
 Ako čitamo

1060
00:55:32,740 --> 00:55:33,860
 i razmatramo

1061
00:55:33,860 --> 00:55:34,500
 o ne znamo

1062
00:55:34,500 --> 00:55:35,240
 istirivanju zloduha,

1063
00:55:35,240 --> 00:55:35,580
 znači,

1064
00:55:35,580 --> 00:55:36,800
 pobjeđuje zloduha.

1065
00:55:37,940 --> 00:55:38,420
 pozdravlja.

1066
00:55:38,420 --> 00:55:40,640
 Pa danas sam slušao

1067
00:55:40,640 --> 00:55:41,740
 Evanđelju o egzorcizmu,

1068
00:55:41,740 --> 00:55:43,120
 pa danas sam slušao

1069
00:55:43,120 --> 00:55:43,960
 Evanđelje da je Isus

1070
00:55:43,960 --> 00:55:44,760
 blagoslovio nekog

1071
00:55:44,760 --> 00:55:45,560
 zaračnika,

1072
00:55:45,560 --> 00:55:47,760
 pa jel ti to treba?

1073
00:55:47,760 --> 00:55:49,680
 Jel znaš neko

1074
00:55:49,680 --> 00:55:50,480
 kome će to trebati?

1075
00:55:50,480 --> 00:55:51,900
 Pa jel to doživljaš

1076
00:55:51,900 --> 00:55:52,240
 da je to,

1077
00:55:52,240 --> 00:55:53,740
 da si ti svjedok toga?

1078
00:55:53,740 --> 00:55:56,120
 Biti kršćanin

1079
00:55:56,120 --> 00:55:57,780
 znači biti svjedok.

1080
00:55:57,780 --> 00:55:58,140
 Znači,

1081
00:55:58,140 --> 00:55:59,020
 on je koji je to doživio.

1082
00:55:59,020 --> 00:56:00,300
 Ne moraš završiti školu

1083
00:56:00,300 --> 00:56:01,000
 da bi bio svjedok,

1084
00:56:01,000 --> 00:56:02,340
 ali biti tamo

1085
00:56:02,340 --> 00:56:03,280
 i doživjeti.

1086
00:56:03,280 --> 00:56:05,260
 Mi nismo svjedoci

1087
00:56:07,940 --> 00:56:08,880
 sam ja pričao,

1088
00:56:08,880 --> 00:56:10,380
 ali nisi svjedok toga

1089
00:56:10,380 --> 00:56:11,260
 da si to doživio.

1090
00:56:11,260 --> 00:56:13,600
 A po Božjoj riječi

1091
00:56:13,600 --> 00:56:14,560
 se sve te stvari

1092
00:56:14,560 --> 00:56:15,540
 ostvaruju.

1093
00:56:15,540 --> 00:56:17,940
 Ostvaruju.

1094
00:56:17,940 --> 00:56:20,060
 Postaješ muž, žena,

1095
00:56:20,060 --> 00:56:21,200
 rekli smo po toj riječi.

1096
00:56:21,200 --> 00:56:22,180
 Po toj riječi

1097
00:56:22,180 --> 00:56:23,080
 ovaj hostija

1098
00:56:23,080 --> 00:56:25,160
 postaje tijelo Kristovo.

1099
00:56:25,160 --> 00:56:27,500
 Po tom imenu Kristovo.

1100
00:56:27,500 --> 00:56:28,860
 Mi zazivamo to ime.

1101
00:56:28,860 --> 00:56:31,920
 Po riječi si postao kršten.

1102
00:56:31,920 --> 00:56:33,260
 Znači,

1103
00:56:33,260 --> 00:56:34,560
 tebi je Duh svijeti

1104
00:56:34,560 --> 00:56:35,420
 istetovirao,

1105
00:56:35,420 --> 00:56:35,700
 ajmo reči,

1106
00:56:35,700 --> 00:56:36,800
 utetovirao tvoje srce

1107
00:56:36,800 --> 00:56:37,480
 ime Isus.

1108
00:56:38,380 --> 00:56:39,080
 Kad jednog dana

1109
00:56:39,080 --> 00:56:39,960
 budeš stajao

1110
00:56:39,960 --> 00:56:41,320
 možda u čekavonici

1111
00:56:41,320 --> 00:56:42,640
 tamo čistilišta

1112
00:56:42,640 --> 00:56:44,020
 i sad čuješ

1113
00:56:44,020 --> 00:56:44,560
 da ono, znaš,

1114
00:56:44,560 --> 00:56:45,560
 koji u onim starim domima

1115
00:56:45,560 --> 00:56:45,960
 zdravlja,

1116
00:56:45,960 --> 00:56:46,640
 ono, znaš,

1117
00:56:46,640 --> 00:56:47,580
 ono govore ti ono prezmjeno,

1118
00:56:47,580 --> 00:56:48,300
 kolak,

1119
00:56:48,300 --> 00:56:48,660
 sad ti ješ,

1120
00:56:48,660 --> 00:56:49,420
 aha, jedneš tamo,

1121
00:56:49,420 --> 00:56:50,040
 ulaziš tamo,

1122
00:56:50,040 --> 00:56:50,740
 guraš se,

1123
00:56:50,740 --> 00:56:51,440
 ljudi svi gledaju

1124
00:56:51,440 --> 00:56:52,800
 kada ješ preko reda

1125
00:56:52,800 --> 00:56:53,700
 dok uđeš tamo

1126
00:56:53,700 --> 00:56:54,340
 na kontrolu.

1127
00:56:54,340 --> 00:56:55,800
 Sad ja tako zamišljam

1128
00:56:55,800 --> 00:56:56,280
 o čistilište,

1129
00:56:56,280 --> 00:56:56,540
 znaš ono,

1130
00:56:56,540 --> 00:56:56,960
 stojiš,

1131
00:56:56,960 --> 00:56:57,780
 ne smiješ sjest,

1132
00:56:57,920 --> 00:56:58,840
 ne znaš koje je na redu,

1133
00:56:58,840 --> 00:56:59,980
 a oni prozivaju

1134
00:56:59,980 --> 00:57:01,080
 jednog na deset godina,

1135
00:57:01,080 --> 00:57:01,420
 onako,

1136
00:57:01,420 --> 00:57:02,360
 to je čistilište

1137
00:57:02,360 --> 00:57:04,320
 i

1138
00:57:04,320 --> 00:57:06,940
 kad budeš u tom čistilištu

1139
00:57:06,940 --> 00:57:08,200
 ili možda će drugačije izgledat

1140
00:57:08,200 --> 00:57:09,200
 i čuješ da neko viče

1141
00:57:09,200 --> 00:57:10,600
 ljubljeni,

1142
00:57:11,040 --> 00:57:11,660
 omiljeni,

1143
00:57:11,660 --> 00:57:12,480
 najdraži,

1144
00:57:12,480 --> 00:57:13,580
 ne gledaj ko je,

1145
00:57:13,580 --> 00:57:14,160
 ti si,

1146
00:57:14,160 --> 00:57:16,040
 ti si,

1147
00:57:16,040 --> 00:57:17,520
 idi tamo,

1148
00:57:17,520 --> 00:57:18,600
 zove tebe,

1149
00:57:18,600 --> 00:57:19,520
 i ono,

1150
00:57:19,520 --> 00:57:19,940
 ja,

1151
00:57:19,940 --> 00:57:21,080
 pogledaj mi što je

1152
00:57:21,080 --> 00:57:21,740
 istatovirano,

1153
00:57:21,740 --> 00:57:22,280
 ljubljeni,

1154
00:57:22,280 --> 00:57:22,620
 onako,

1155
00:57:22,620 --> 00:57:23,020
 piše,

1156
00:57:23,020 --> 00:57:24,660
 i to ugravirano

1157
00:57:24,660 --> 00:57:25,620
 Isusovom krvlju,

1158
00:57:25,620 --> 00:57:26,980
 onako,

1159
00:57:26,980 --> 00:57:27,520
 ljubljeni,

1160
00:57:27,520 --> 00:57:28,540
 nisam znao,

1161
00:57:28,540 --> 00:57:28,720
 pa,

1162
00:57:28,720 --> 00:57:30,500
 nis primijeti,

1163
00:57:30,500 --> 00:57:31,180
 pa nisam,

1164
00:57:31,180 --> 00:57:31,520
 eto,

1165
00:57:31,520 --> 00:57:32,380
 da,

1166
00:57:32,380 --> 00:57:33,360
 pa mogo sam i priući,

1167
00:57:33,360 --> 00:57:33,960
 pa mogo si,

1168
00:57:33,960 --> 00:57:35,480
 onda mogo si,

1169
00:57:35,480 --> 00:57:37,120
 mogo si.

1170
00:57:37,120 --> 00:57:39,160
 Braćovi sestre,

1171
00:57:39,160 --> 00:57:41,000
 riječ je neopisivo,

1172
00:57:41,040 --> 00:57:41,920
 snažna,

1173
00:57:41,920 --> 00:57:42,540
 duboka,

1174
00:57:42,540 --> 00:57:43,580
 ona je ogledalo,

1175
00:57:43,580 --> 00:57:46,000
 ona je ogledalo,

1176
00:57:46,000 --> 00:57:46,920
 tvoje moje duše,

1177
00:57:46,920 --> 00:57:49,040
 ona daje to svjetlost,

1178
00:57:49,040 --> 00:57:50,540
 ona ti daje snagu,

1179
00:57:50,540 --> 00:57:51,220
 i gled,

1180
00:57:51,220 --> 00:57:53,680
 neke stvari su možda jednostavnije,

1181
00:57:53,680 --> 00:57:54,800
 pa je dovoljno malo riječi,

1182
00:57:54,800 --> 00:57:56,220
 a neke treba malo više,

1183
00:57:56,220 --> 00:57:59,100
 negdje treba malo više dublje zakopat,

1184
00:57:59,100 --> 00:58:01,240
 malo više razmatrat,

1185
00:58:01,240 --> 00:58:02,760
 malo više to prolazit,

1186
00:58:02,760 --> 00:58:05,720
 malo više se tome prepustit,

1187
00:58:05,720 --> 00:58:08,200
 jer gospodin želi ozbiljnost,

1188
00:58:08,200 --> 00:58:09,060
 ozbiljnost.

1189
00:58:10,160 --> 00:58:11,420
 njega ne možeš prevariti s time,

1190
00:58:11,420 --> 00:58:13,200
 nije da mi sad želimo prevariti,

1191
00:58:13,200 --> 00:58:13,780
 ali nije ona sad,

1192
00:58:13,780 --> 00:58:14,600
 a dobro,

1193
00:58:14,600 --> 00:58:14,880
 eto,

1194
00:58:14,880 --> 00:58:15,840
 malo ću krunicu izmojiti,

1195
00:58:15,840 --> 00:58:17,040
 pa ajde neku devetnicu,

1196
00:58:17,040 --> 00:58:17,520
 super,

1197
00:58:17,520 --> 00:58:19,600
 budi vjerom toj devetnici,

1198
00:58:19,600 --> 00:58:22,600
 ali prvo razlučiš šta gospodin želi.

1199
00:58:22,600 --> 00:58:24,980
 To je vrlo praktično i super je,

1200
00:58:24,980 --> 00:58:25,360
 zašto?

1201
00:58:25,360 --> 00:58:26,820
 Ti možeš doći,

1202
00:58:26,820 --> 00:58:27,400
 sad tražiti,

1203
00:58:27,400 --> 00:58:29,320
 ja dolazim iz župe svjetog Antuna Padovanskog,

1204
00:58:29,320 --> 00:58:30,500
 u selima svesvjetskim,

1205
00:58:30,500 --> 00:58:31,440
 i onda tamo ljudi dolaze,

1206
00:58:31,440 --> 00:58:32,600
 pante, testovi,

1207
00:58:32,600 --> 00:58:33,480
 pante, muž,

1208
00:58:33,560 --> 00:58:34,420
 pante, žena,

1209
00:58:34,420 --> 00:58:36,660
 pa onda devetnici,

1210
00:58:36,660 --> 00:58:38,600
 13 utoraka svjeto Antipa,

1211
00:58:38,600 --> 00:58:39,140
 ljudi moji,

1212
00:58:39,140 --> 00:58:40,460
 znaš šta treba to izdržati.

1213
00:58:40,460 --> 00:58:42,100
 I onda još ne dođe,

1214
00:58:42,100 --> 00:58:42,640
 pa dođe,

1215
00:58:42,640 --> 00:58:43,500
 pa ovako, pa nakako,

1216
00:58:43,500 --> 00:58:44,000
 Bogu hvala,

1217
00:58:44,000 --> 00:58:44,180
 ajde,

1218
00:58:44,180 --> 00:58:44,880
 ima pomaka,

1219
00:58:44,880 --> 00:58:45,740
 ali ono,

1220
00:58:45,740 --> 00:58:46,380
 to je trud,

1221
00:58:46,380 --> 00:58:47,300
 to je teret,

1222
00:58:47,300 --> 00:58:47,760
 jer ono,

1223
00:58:47,760 --> 00:58:49,520
 pokušavaš na govorit duha svjetoga,

1224
00:58:49,520 --> 00:58:50,700
 da ti nešto napravi,

1225
00:58:50,700 --> 00:58:51,400
 oj, neće,

1226
00:58:51,480 --> 00:58:52,320
 koji ima neke svoje,

1227
00:58:52,320 --> 00:58:52,780
 pa ajde,

1228
00:58:52,780 --> 00:58:54,700
 a kaže ti Isus,

1229
00:58:54,700 --> 00:58:56,440
 ma ostavi to,

1230
00:58:56,440 --> 00:58:58,580
 nego kaže,

1231
00:58:58,580 --> 00:58:58,760
 gledaj,

1232
00:58:58,760 --> 00:58:58,940
 ajde,

1233
00:58:58,940 --> 00:59:00,180
 napravi meni jednu uslugu,

1234
00:59:00,180 --> 00:59:03,340
 sad meni se ta usluga Isusu ne sviđa,

1235
00:59:03,340 --> 00:59:03,920
 ali ajde,

1236
00:59:03,920 --> 00:59:04,360
 Isuse,

1237
00:59:04,360 --> 00:59:05,480
 kad je tebi usluga,

1238
00:59:05,480 --> 00:59:06,000
 ajde,

1239
00:59:06,000 --> 00:59:07,460
 i sad Isus ti kaže,

1240
00:59:07,460 --> 00:59:07,600
 gledaj,

1241
00:59:07,600 --> 00:59:08,860
 usluga ti je daj ovom sirmahu,

1242
00:59:08,860 --> 00:59:09,740
 daj nešto pojesti,

1243
00:59:09,740 --> 00:59:10,240
 ajde,

1244
00:59:10,240 --> 00:59:12,160
 i ti to njemu daš pojesti,

1245
00:59:12,160 --> 00:59:12,840
 a Isus ti gleda,

1246
00:59:12,840 --> 00:59:14,020
 ma sine,

1247
00:59:14,020 --> 00:59:14,660
 hvala ti,

1248
00:59:14,660 --> 00:59:16,240
 ili mogu da za tebe jednu uslugu učiniti?

1249
00:59:17,140 --> 00:59:18,620
 Pa, kad si već pito,

1250
00:59:18,620 --> 00:59:22,100
 učini uslugu Isusu,

1251
00:59:22,100 --> 00:59:25,180
 znači uopće nemoj ići raditi ono što bi ti htio,

1252
00:59:25,180 --> 00:59:26,280
 ne kažem da je to loše,

1253
00:59:26,280 --> 00:59:26,500
 ne,

1254
00:59:26,500 --> 00:59:29,220
 ali to ti je gubljenje vremena,

1255
00:59:29,220 --> 00:59:31,020
 nego stani,

1256
00:59:31,020 --> 00:59:31,880
 idi na džokera,

1257
00:59:31,880 --> 00:59:32,460
 idi na ono,

1258
00:59:32,460 --> 00:59:33,140
 idi na sigurno,

1259
00:59:33,140 --> 00:59:33,640
 idi na ono,

1260
00:59:33,640 --> 00:59:34,260
 idi na milion,

1261
00:59:34,260 --> 00:59:35,540
 idi i treba čekaj,

1262
00:59:35,540 --> 00:59:36,520
 gospodine,

1263
00:59:36,520 --> 00:59:37,380
 daj, evo,

1264
00:59:37,380 --> 00:59:39,840
 ima li neka usluga koju ja za tebe danas mogu učiniti?

1265
00:59:39,840 --> 00:59:41,340
 Mogu li ja nešto,

1266
00:59:41,340 --> 00:59:41,560
 evo,

1267
00:59:41,560 --> 00:59:43,960
 da se tebi svidi nešto što tebi treba Isuse?

1268
00:59:44,540 --> 00:59:46,080
 je li treba nekog potapšat,

1269
00:59:46,080 --> 00:59:46,660
 ušamarit,

1270
00:59:46,660 --> 00:59:47,320
 nahranit,

1271
00:59:47,320 --> 00:59:48,060
 povuć,

1272
00:59:48,060 --> 00:59:48,580
 prevest,

